videos.headline: Brooks sacks McGough
videos.description: Khalil Brooks goes through the line unblocked to sack Alex McGough.

videos.headline: Thomas dives into end zone for TD
videos.description: Wildcat QB Tavares Thomas dives over the line for a 1-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Thomas spins into end zone for TD
videos.description: Tavares Thomas uses a spin move to get into the end zone for his second touchdown.

videos.headline: McGough runs for 13-yard TD
videos.description: Quarterback Alex McGough takes it himself to score FIU's first touchdown of the game.

videos.headline: Thomas runs for his 3rd TD
videos.description: Linebacker/ Wildcat Quarterback Tavares Thomas scores his third touchdown of the game on 4-yard run.

videos.headline: Ferguson grabs INT off tipped pass
videos.description: Alex McGough has his pass intercepted by Jordan Ferguson after the ball is tipped in the air.

videos.headline: Winning the turnover battle is key
videos.description: Head Coach Rick Stocksill tells Sara Cardona that his team was better offensively because they did not turn the ball over in Middle Tennessee's 37-17 win over Florida International.
